description: Every Runner experiences some low days when he/she needs just a little push to get out there and sweat out a run. Running Guru tells inspirational quotes to motivate runners to go for their runs. Just ask Alexa to tell Running Guru to tell me something or inspire me or motivate me.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Running Guru to inspire me.
Alexa ask Running Guru to motivate me.
Alexa ask Running Guru for motivation.
name: Running Guru
shortDescription: Running Guru inspires you to get out and run.
